CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: GCI Liberty, Inc. (Nasdaq: GLIBA, GLIBP) operates and owns interests in a broad range of communications businesses. GCI Liberty's assets consist of its subsidiary GCI Holdings, LLC ("GCI") and interests in Charter Communications, Liberty Broadband Corporation and Lending Tree. GCI is Alaska's largest communications provider, providing data, wireless, video, voice and managed services to consumer and business customers throughout Alaska and nationwide. GCI has delivered services for nearly 40 years to some of the most remote communities and in some of the most challenging conditions in North America.
